name: A Million Voices Crying Out
Lore: 'Tarkin silenced the voices of Alderaan with the power of the Death Star.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Twice per game may take Commence Primary Ignition into hand from Lost Pile or Reserve Deck; reshuffle. If Alderaan ''blown away,'' retrieve 3 Force whenever you deploy a unique (•) Star Destroyer. (Immune to Alter.)',
